(156, 'ps_option', 'a:34:{s:8:\"last_tab\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"of_logo\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:62:\"http://coktilat.com/wp-content/themes/coktilat/images/logo.png\";s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:0:\"\";}s:8:\"overview\";s:578:\"<blockquote>\r\n<h3>Coktilat<strong>, your friend in the business world!</strong></h3>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">Providing the efficiencies, Professional services, Integrated solutions, Outsourcing, Multiple areas, Full responsibility in providing the services.</span></h3>\";s:8:\"about_us\";s:374:\"A Company specialized in providing the best efficiency in all areas of work for entrepreneurs in the world, our responsibility is to provide an integrated and multidisciplinary services of the management, follow up and developing the performance of the service, helping you as an entrepreneur to focus on your company earnings and assume the functions of your business side.\";s:13:\"earnings_desc\";s:143:\"Don\'t waste time in following up the business side, let us handle the task. Only focus on your basic business value and increase your profits.\";s:14:\"coktailer_desc\";s:932:\"<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Do you have passion towards your skills? Creativity and challenging are part of your character? Always ready to be one of those who achieved successful projects?</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black;\">Contact us:</span> Your coming world <strong>Coktilat<span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\">.</span></strong></p>\";s:12:\"contact_desc\";s:1244:\"<h3>We can help your business with our knowledge</h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: normal;\">We have passion, challenge and skill to make real success stories from business<span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\">.</span></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\"> </span></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 107%; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Coktilat </span></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 107%;  color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">are the chance that gives you the ability to focus your efforts well on your business.</span></blockquote>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: left;\"></p>\";s:5:\"email\";s:17:\"info@coktilat.com\";s:5:\"phone\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:15:\" ©Coktilat2019\";s:12:\"contact_form\";s:46:\"[contact-form-7 id=\"5\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]\";s:9:\"hire_form\";s:40:\"[contact-form-7 id=\"57\" title=\"Hire Us\"]\";s:9:\"join_form\";s:42:\"[contact-form-7 id=\"62\" title=\"Join Form\"]\";s:15:\"Client_Form_new\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"of_facebook\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"of_twitter\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"of_gplus\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"of_instagram\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"of_linkedin\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"of_youtube\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"of_whatsapp\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"overview_ar\";s:324:\"&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h3>كوكتيلات... <strong>صديقك في عالم الأعمال</strong>!</h3>\r\n</blockquote>\r\nتوفير أفضل الكفاءات، خدمات احترافية، عمل عن بعد، حلول متكاملة، مجالات متعددة، مسئولية كاملة عن تقديم الخدمة.\";s:11:\"about_us_ar\";s:467:\"شركة متخصصة في تقديم أفضل الكفاءات في جميع مجالات العمل عن بعد لأصحاب الأعمال في العالم، مسئوليتنا تقديم خدمات متكاملة ومتعددة التخصصات من إدارة، ومتابعة، وتطوير أداء الخدمة،\r\n\r\nنساعدك كصاحب عمل للتركيز على إيرادات شركتك ونتحمل مهام عملك التجاري الجانبية.\";s:16:\"earnings_desc_ar\";s:217:\"لا تضع الوقت في متابعة الأعمال الجانبية، دعنا نتولى المهمة، فقط ركز على القيمة الأساسية لمشروعك التجاري وزيادة أرباحك.\";s:17:\"coktailer_desc_ar\";s:298:\"<blockquote>تملك الشغف تجاه مهارتك، التحدي والإبداع من شخصيتك، مثابر ومستعد لتكون أحد أبطال نجاح المشاريع.</blockquote>\r\n<strong> تواصل معنا</strong>، <strong>كوكتيلات عالمك القادم</strong>.\";s:15:\"contact_desc_ar\";s:451:\"<blockquote><strong>يمكننا دعم عملك التجاري بخبرتنا ومعرفتنا</strong></blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">نملك الشغف والتحدي والمهارة لنصنع من الأعمال التجارية قصص نجاح حقيقية.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">كوكتيلات الفرصة لتركيز جهودك جيدًا في عملك التجاري.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\";s:12:\"copyright_ar\";s:23:\" ©كوكتيلات2019\";s:15:\"contact_form_ar\";s:53:\"[contact-form-7 id=\"142\" title=\"تواصل معنا\"]\";s:12:\"hire_form_ar\";s:50:\"[contact-form-7 id=\"143\" title=\"استأجرنا\"]\";s:12:\"join_form_ar\";s:21:\"كن كوكتيلًا\";s:14:\"client_form_ar\";s:57:\"[contact-form-7 id=\"141\" title=\"نموذج العميل\"]\";s:15:\"hire_form_title\";s:88:\"<h3> 😊 كوكتيلات بانتظارك</h3>\r\n🏆 لنصنع النجاح معًا\";s:15:\"join_form_title\";s:82:\"<h3> Be Coktailer 😎 </h3>\r\n\r\n<strong>Coktilat:</strong> your coming world 🤩\";s:17:\"client_form_title\";s:67:\"<h3>Focus on your profit!</h3>\r\n\r\nLet\'s doing success together 🏆\";}', 'yes'),
